<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='880348' id='t-880348'>but we might also be able to change</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='882129' id='t-882129'>the way we relate to each other</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='883892' id='t-883892'>and the way we relate to 
