<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='887003' id='t-887003'>And to me, that's absolutely</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='889051' id='t-889051'>worth trying for.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='890622' id='t-890622'>Thank you very much.</span>
